      "id": "PopularPost273485",
      "post_content": "i played prerelease with izzet and splashed black. lost my first game and I looked through my cards again. I saw this guy, took out something terrible that didn't work that game, and stuck him in.  \n  \nFinished 3-1. Every game I drew him early I won, because his 4 toughness at only 2 mana allowed me to stabilize from early threats (and there are a surprising amount of 1-3 power creatures). In one game my opponent got mana flooded when I dropped him early, then I killed his creatures and this finished him.",
