    {
      "id": "PopularPost274622",
      "post_content": "Honestly, I like this guy a lot, even for standard.   \n  \nWith Aggro strategies becoming more and more popular, this guy as a 1/4 for two CMC gives any mid-range or control deck a way to survive (and kill) Gravecrawler and diregraf ghoul. Also it acts as a good constant blocker against Geralf's Messenger without having to kill the thing and trigger undying. Further it blocks centaurs and other Selysnia tokens. All in all I think this is a solid durdle card.   \n  \nAs for offense, it does provide some early game damage out put if your opponent is running low, and will win a race in certain circumstances. ",
      "posted_by": "GabrielAothin",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost274622\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">Honestly, I like this guy a lot, even for standard. <br/><br/>With Aggro strategies becoming more and more popular, this guy as a 1/4 for two CMC gives any mid-range or control deck a way to survive (and kill) Gravecrawler and diregraf ghoul. Also it acts as a good constant blocker against Geralf's Messenger without having to kill the thing and trigger undying. Further it blocks centaurs and other Selysnia tokens. All in all I think this is a solid durdle card. <br/><br/>As for offense, it does provide some early game damage out put if your opponent is running low, and will win a race in certain circumstances.  </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '274622'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy77642\">GabrielAothin</span>\r\n                                (10/7/2012 11:27:47 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postRati