    {
      "id": "PopularPost316110",
      "post_content": "Nice little \"wall\" to endure the first assoult of aggro decks, and can survive a lot of red board sweeps, like [Pyroclasm](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pyroclasm), [Volcanic Fallout](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Volcanic Fallout), [Slagstorm](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Slagstorm), so you can block with this and, after your opponent build quite an army to pass thought this Weird, you can sweep without losing your \"wall\". In some occasion, you could even attack with this, and deliver some damages...  \nSo:  \n-can block and survive and/or kill the attacker  \n-can attack for 4  \n-can survive most common damage-based board sweepers  \n-it's a Weird!  \n  \nI waited for so long for such efficient creature in {R/U}. I think it should deserve a little more love, even for constructed...  \n  \n4.5/5",
      "posted_by": "leomistico",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost316110\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">Nice little \"wall\" to endure the first assoult of aggro decks, and can survive a lot of red board sweeps, like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Pyroclasm\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pyroclasm\">Pyroclasm</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Volcanic Fallout\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Volcanic Fallout\">Volcanic Fallout</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Slagstorm\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Slagstorm\">Slagstorm</a>, so you can block with this and, after your opponent build quite an army to pass thought this Weird, you can sweep without losing your \"wall\". In some occasion, you could even attack with this, and deliver some damages...<br/>So:<br/>-can block and survive and/or kill the attacker<br/>-can attack for 4<br/>-can survive most common damage-based board sweepers<br/>-it's a Weird!<br/><br/>I waited for so long for such efficient creature in {R/U}. I think it should deserve a little more love, even for constructed...<br/><br/>4.5/5</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '316110'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy822\">leomistico</span>\r\n                    